parameters:
Phew... Phew...! As expected, heavy labor is tough on this
old body...! If I didn't have my hot pack, my back would be
ruined...!

If I could save those children... I could say I had a good
life. Please, I beg of you... Laura-sama... Vega-sama...
Did you... set fire...? How thorough...!

Goodness... To go through the trouble of cremating me...!
The King of Cordain is quite considerate...!

Grandma... Cecil...! It's about time for me to... go over
there too...
